 - `1 <= n, m <= 10^5`
 - `1 <= n * m <= 10^5`
 - `1 <= sources.length <= n * m`
 - `sources[i] = [r_i, c_i, color_i]`
 - `0 <= r_i <= n - 1`
 - `0 <= c_i <= m - 1`
 - `1 <= color_i <= 10^6​​​​​​​`
